Question: What watercraft has the same color as the shirts in this image?

Reference Answer: boats

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n507959.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=EVAL(expr="[[0,0,{IMAGE.size[0]}-1,{IMAGE.size[1]}-1]]")
IMAGE0=CROP_ABOVE(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='shirts')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What color are the shirts?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE,question='What watercraft is in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
